import React from 'react';
import { Box, Container, Typography, Grid, Paper } from '@mui/material';

function Dashboard() {
  return (
    <Container>
      <Box sx={{ py: 4 }}>
        <Typography variant="h4" sx={{ mb: 4 }}>Dashboard Admin</Typography>
        
        <Grid container spacing={3}>
          <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
            <Paper sx={{ p: 3 }}>
              <Typography variant="h6">Total Check-In</Typography>
              <Typography variant="h3">15</Typography>
            </Paper>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
            <Paper sx={{ p: 3 }}>
              <Typography variant="h6">Total Check-Out</Typography>
              <Typography variant="h3">12</Typography>
            </Paper>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12}>
            <Paper sx={{ p: 3, mt: 3 }}>
              <Typography variant="h6" sx={{ mb: 2 }}>Daftar Pengunjung</Typography>
              {/* Tabel pengunjung akan ditambahkan di sini */}
            </Paper>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </Box>
    </Container>
  );
}

export default Dashboard;
